# Task 1 - ALU Design
## overview
This project implements a 4-bit Arithmetic Logic Unit (ALU) using verilog.
## Operations Performed
- Addition
- Subtraction
- AND
- OR
-  NOT
## Files Included
- alu.v -> Main ALU design code
- alu_tb.v -> Testbench for simulation
- ALU_waveform.png -> Simulation waveform output
## Tools Used
- EDA Playground
## Learning Outcome
Learned combinational circuit design, testbench creation, waveform generation, and debugging in Verilog.
